default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThroughout undergraduate 
defaultstudy
default, steps should be taken by institutions and by individual 
defaultuniversity 
defaultdepartments and schools to make 
defaultclear to female science students that their contribution is valued entirely on a par with that of their male counterparts. Any 
defaultsuggestion of gende
defaultr 
defaultbias in the culture should be addressed at this early stage by thoroughgoing equality and diversity training
default for all staff and by having a system that offer
defaults
default support if ever such bias, or indeed discrimination of any kind, seems to manifest itself.
default A contribution towards this would be an ‘inclusive curriculum’ aiming
default 
defaultto support academic schools in reviewing the 
defaultinclusivity and accessibility of their practices in learning, teaching and assessment, and in implementing an action plan to promote equality.
default11
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIt goes without saying that this culture should continue at postgraduate level, since this is the point at which 
defaultmany female students will decid
defaulte
